ustom AttributeImpl subclasses for Lucene 6.0.0 by implementing reflectWith(AttributeReflector); the pre-6 default reflection behavior is no longer available.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Adding lucene-analyzers-common or other Lucene modules is not required for core-only reachability coverage and may unnecessarily broaden the workflow scope.\",\n    \"If the JVM opens are dropped, tests covering MMapDirectory/RamUsageEstimator internals may fail or avoid the reachability paths already covered by the existing scaffold.\",\n    \"The reported compile failure is an API change in AttributeImpl, not evidence of a missing dependency or Docker service.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_001ce65c1845face016a40014379948194bdb04a94b445b284\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 5207, "output": 797, "cacheRead": 35840, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 41844, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782579514435, "responseId": "resp_001ce65c1845face016a40013ae6cc81948a7c3a2802ce81a3"}}
